snippet.description:
Overcast at This Is Hardcore (July 24, 2014) filmed at The Electric Factory in Philadelphia, PA by Hate5Six.com
Additional camerawork by Steven Cergizan
Mixed and Mastered by Len Carmichael in Ewing, NJ 

Bullet Tooth is excited to announce the 3x CD Discography "Only Death Is Smiling" from Massachusetts' metal legends OVERCAST! The band started in the early 90s long before the explosion of metal from the New England area, and released a few albums on indie labels until the late 90s when they broke up to focus on new bands like SHADOWS FALL and KILLSWITCH ENGAGE, and more recently, DEATH RAY VISION.

Pre-Orders for the Overcast 3X CD Discography “Only Death Is Smiling” (Out February 3) are up now! Get the CD with FREE posters, or with an exclusive new shirt, or the mega bundle with a Limited Edition skate deck!  http://www.BulletTooth.com/store

Overcast on tour!
Jan 29 – Boston, MA @ The Middle East w/ PanzerBastard 
Jan 30 – Providence, RI @ The Ruins w/ Empire Shall Fall 
Jan 31 – Worcester, MA @ Ralph’s Dinner w/ Empire Shall Fall 
Feb 01 - Worcester, MA @ The Middle East w/ Dissolve
April 17 - Worcester, MA @ New England Metal Fest

Overcast is:
Brian Fair: Vocals
Mike D’Antonio: Bass
Pete Cortese: Guitar
Scott McCooe: Guitar
Jay Fitzgerald: Drums
 
For More Info:
http://www.Facebook.com/OvercastMA
